dct_title_s: Automobile route from Los Angeles to San Francisco via coast route
dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; AB.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Orientated with north toward upper right.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, drainage, vegetation.
Indicates distances from Los Angeles and San Francisco.
Numbered 144 in lower left corner, 7 in top right corner, and 97 in bottom margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
